data.description: Located in the sought-after Merrifields neighborhood, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom brick home impeccably maintained and boasting a sleek modern feel, featuring recent upgrades including new black stainless steel appliances that bring both style and functionality to the heart of the home. Enter inside to discover the luxury of brand new LVP flooring, a freshly installed water heater, and a new electric panel, ensuring efficiency and comfort at every turn. Backyard – an entertainer's paradise complete with an inviting in-ground pool featuring a new liner with salt system, all surrounded by a sprawling yard perfect for summer BBQs & gatherings and wired for adding a hot tub. Plus, with French drains keeping the area dry and a meticulously maintained crawl space complete with encapsulation and a dehumidifier, this home is as efficient as it is stylish. Picture yourself unwinding by the firepit on cool evenings or basking in the sunlight from the comfort of the sunroom.
